description: Permanently deletes a  RegexPatternSet. You can't delete a RegexPatternSet if it's still used in any RegexMatchSet or if the RegexPatternSet is not empty.

parameters.name: RegexPatternSetId
parameters.description: The RegexPatternSetId of the  RegexPatternSet that you want to delete. RegexPatternSetId is returned by  CreateRegexPatternSet and by  ListRegexPatternSets.

parameters.name: ChangeToken
parameters.description: The value returned by the most recent call to  GetChangeToken.

nested_items.name: ChangeToken
nested_items.description: The ChangeToken that you used to submit the DeleteRegexPatternSet request. You can also use this value to query the status of the request. For more information, see  GetChangeTokenStatus.
